# Docker ignore file for AG News Text Classification
# ================================================================================
# Excludes unnecessary files from Docker build context to improve build speed
# and reduce image size
#
# References:
#   - Docker .dockerignore: https://docs.docker.com/engine/reference/builder/#dockerignore-file
#   - Build Context Best Practices: https://docs.docker.com/develop/develop-images/dockerfile_best-practices/#exclude-with-dockerignore
#
# Author: Võ Hải Dũng
# License: MIT

